🧩 Criticism is a puzzle piece that helps complete the bigger picture!  
👉 Tip: Create an environment where constructive criticism is welcomed. It leads to growth and continuous improvement.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
